== 诊断与治疗 ==
猪蛔虫病的临床表现症状有咳嗽， 呼吸急促， 神情憔悴，腹绞痛， 体重减轻或体重增加减慢。 对蛔虫病的诊断可通过漂浮法对宿主的粪便进行检查或通过临床症状进行检查确认。一般利用{{link-en|驱蛔虫药|Ascaricide}}进行治疗。

== 事件 ==
1970年在加拿大， 一位博士后研究人员用猪蛔虫污染了室友的食物。 事件导致四名受害者患重病，其中导致二人急性呼吸衰竭。<ref>{{Cite journal|author = James A. Phills, A. John Harrold, Gabriel V. Whiteman & Lewis Perelmutter|year = 1972|title = Pulmonary infiltrates, asthma and eosinophilia due to ''Ascaris suum'' infestation in man|journal = [[New_England_Journal_of_Medicine|New England Journal of Medicine]]|volume = 286|issue = |pages = 965–970|pmid = 5062734|url = http://www.k-state.edu/parasitology/articles/ascariasis.pdf|format = [[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]]|doi = 10.1056/NEJM197205042861802|access-date = 2015-09-14|archive-date = 2016-03-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234321/http://www.k-state.edu/parasitology/articles/ascariasis.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.cfsan.fda.gov/~dms/rabtact.html|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090527230939/http://www.cfsan.fda.gov/~dms/rabtact.html|archivedate = 2009年5月27日|title = Risk Assessment for Food Terrorism and Other Food Safety Concerns|publisher = [[Food_and_Drug_Administration|Food and Drug Administration]] [[Center_for_Food_Safety_and_Applied_Nutrition|Center for Food Safety and Applied Nutrition]]|date = October 13, 2003|accessdate = February 15, 2012|deadurl = yes}}</ref>

